  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Max Ranks</strong>: 5</p><hr /><p>A Slowed creature feels as though they are in slow motion, akin to walking in water, preventing them from battling at their usual combat pace.</p><ul><li><p>A Slowed creature has its speed reduced by 10 for each rank it has and cannot gain bonuses to speed for the duration.</p></li><li><p>A Slowed creature can never make more than one attack, or cast more than 1 jutsu, per turn.</p></li><li><p>The slowed condition last for the duration of the original jutsu or 1 minute has passed, whichever comes first.</p></li></ul>",
